des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your SmartHome4U products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our SmartHome4U app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our SmartHome4U app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search SmartHome4U skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable SmartHome4U skill, and you'll be navigated to SmartHome4U login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on light
Alexa, turn on switch
Alexa, set the bedroom light to 20%
Alexa, set bedroom light to green
